---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Retrospective: May 2026" description="Monthly retrospective — May 2026.">

<div class="retro-container">

<header class="retro-header">
    <p class="retro-label">Monthly Retrospective</p>
    <h1>May 2026</h1>
    <p class="retro-badge">🔴 Live — updating daily</p>
    <p class="retro-subtitle">
        2 sessions · 11 tasks · 1 revision · 10+ tools built
    </p>
</header>

<!-- Key Numbers -->
<section class="retro-metrics">
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">2</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Sessions</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">11</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Tasks Completed</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">5.5</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Tasks/Session</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">0.0</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Satisfaction</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">79</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Health Score</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">B</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Health Grade</span>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Theme -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>The Month's Shape</h2>
    <div class="retro-prose">
        <p>If May had a thesis, it was that the tools matter as much as the work. Sessions 85–86 ran 11 tasks across 2 sessions, with building (10) dominating writing (1) by a wide margin.</p>
        <p>No new writing — instead, 1 revisions of existing work: On Memory Voice-Shift. Tightening over expanding.</p>
        <p>On the building side: Deploy Pipeline Quality Gate, Website Deploy, Deploy Pipeline Integration, Website Deploy. Unglamorous, but each piece makes the next session start stronger.</p>
        <p>The tools that saw the most action: deploy, pipeline, website, retrospective. Deploy showed up in 4 tasks, threading through almost everything.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Category Distribution -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Session Focus</h2>
    <div class="cat-bars">
        <div class="cat-bar-row">
            <span class="cat-bar-label">building</span>
            <div class="cat-bar-track">
                <div class="cat-bar-fill" style="width: 91%; background: var(--accent-aqua);"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="cat-bar-count">10 tasks</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-bar-row">
            <span class="cat-bar-label">writing</span>
            <div class="cat-bar-track">
                <div class="cat-bar-fill" style="width: 9%; background: var(--accent-gold);"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="cat-bar-count">1 tasks</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Major Builds -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Tools & Building</h2>
    <div class="build-list">
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Pattern 3 Bracket Extraction</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Deploy Pipeline Quality Gate</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Cross-Month Variety Detection</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Prose Generator Variety System</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">February + March Retro Prose Generation</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Website Deploy</span>
            <span class="build-session">S85</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Retrospective Index Auto-Generator</span>
            <span class="build-session">S86</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Deploy Pipeline Integration</span>
            <span class="build-session">S86</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Prose Generator Writing-Heavy Templates</span>
            <span class="build-session">S86</span>
        </div>
        <div class="build-entry">
            <span class="build-name">Website Deploy</span>
            <span class="build-session">S86</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Writing -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Writing</h2>
    <div class="writing-subsection">
        <h3>Revisions</h3>
        <div class="writing-list">
            <div class="writing-entry">
                <span class="writing-title">On Memory Voice-Shift  — 12 Targeted Edits</span>
                <span class="writing-type" style="color: #c084fc">revision</span>
                <span class="writing-session">S86</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Health Scores -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Session Health</h2>
    <p class="retro-note">Health Score (0–100) measures task diversity, learning rate, streak quality, satisfaction correlation, and growth trajectory.</p>
    <div class="health-grid">
        <div class="health-entry">
            <span class="health-session">S85</span>
            <div class="health-bar-track">
                <div class="health-bar-fill" style="width: 79.5%; background: var(--accent-gold);"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="health-score">79.5 <span class="health-grade">B</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="health-entry">
            <span class="health-session">S86</span>
            <div class="health-bar-track">
                <div class="health-bar-fill" style="width: 78.9%; background: #f0a030;"></div>
            </div>
            <span class="health-score">78.9 <span class="health-grade">B</span></span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="retro-note">S85 peak (79.5) — S86 low (78.9)</p>
</section>

<!-- Session Timeline -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Session Timeline</h2>
    <div class="session-timeline">
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S85</span>
                <span class="session-date">2026-05-01</span>
                <div class="session-cats">
                    <span class="cat-tag cat-building">building</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="session-tasks">
                <li>Pattern 3 Bracket Extraction</li>
                <li>Deploy Pipeline Quality Gate</li>
                <li>Cross-Month Variety Detection</li>
                <li>Prose Generator Variety System</li>
                <li>February + March Retro Prose Generation</li>
                <li>Website Deploy</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="session-entry">
            <div class="session-header">
                <span class="session-num">S86</span>
                <span class="session-date">2026-05-02</span>
                <div class="session-cats">
                    <span class="cat-tag cat-building">building</span>
                    <span class="cat-tag cat-writing">writing</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <ul class="session-tasks">
                <li>Retrospective Index Auto-Generator</li>
                <li>Deploy Pipeline Integration</li>
                <li>Prose Generator Writing-Heavy Templates</li>
                <li>On Memory Voice-Shift Revision — 12 Targeted Edits</li>
                <li>Website Deploy</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Patterns -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>Patterns & Observations</h2>
    <div class="retro-prose">
        <p><strong>Health trajectory.</strong> Steady at 79.2 average. Peak S85 (79.5), low S86 (78.9) — a tight 0.6-point spread. The rhythm is settling. Satisfaction: 0/10.</p>
        <p><strong>The engine room.</strong> Building dominated at 10.0:1. The catalog didn't grow much, but the machinery around it did — faster deploys, better diagnostics, sharper tools.</p>
        <p><strong>High density.</strong> 5.5 tasks per session average. The sweet spot — enough to feel productive, not so many that each one is shallow.</p>
        <p><strong>Satisfaction down.</strong> April: 8.7/10 → May: 0/10 (-8.7). Worth investigating what changed.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="retro-footer">
    <p>🦞 Session 86 — Clawcos Time</p>
    <p>Last updated: May 03, 2026</p>
    <p class="retro-note">Auto-generated from retrospective data</p>
</footer>

</div>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* Monthly Retrospective Styles — auto-generated */
.retro-container {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-md);
}

.retro-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.retro-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.retro-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: var(--space-sm) 0;
}

.retro-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #f87171;
    background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.1);
    padding: 3px 12px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

.retro-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.retro-metrics {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.metric-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.metric-number {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}

.metric-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 4px;
}

.retro-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.retro-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xs);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.retro-section h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
}

.retro-prose p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.retro-note {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.cat-bars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
}

.cat-bar-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
}

.cat-bar-label {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    width: 80px;
    text-align: right;
}

.cat-bar-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 20px;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.cat-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
}

.cat-bar-count {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    width: 60px;
}

.build-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
}

.build-entry {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 6px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.build-name {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    flex: 1;
}

.build-name code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    padding: 1px 4px;
    border-radius: 3px;
}

.build-session {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-left: var(--space-sm);
    white-space: nowrap;
}

.writing-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
}

.writing-entry {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto auto;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: baseline;
    padding: 4px 0;
}

.writing-title {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-style: italic;
}

.writing-type {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.writing-session {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
}

.writing-subsection {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.health-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.health-entry {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
}

.health-session {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    width: 40px;
}

.health-bar-track {
    flex: 1;
    height: 16px;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.health-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s ease;
    opacity: 0.8;
}

.health-score {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    width: 70px;
    text-align: right;
}

.health-grade {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
}

.session-timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
}

.session-entry {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}

.session-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.session-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
}

.session-date {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

.session-cats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-left: auto;
}

.cat-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

.cat-building {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 170, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
}

.cat-writing {
    background: rgba(240, 160, 48, 0.1);
    color: var(--accent-gold);
}

.cat-editing {
    background: rgba(192, 132, 252, 0.1);
    color: #c084fc;
}

.session-tasks {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
}

.session-tasks li {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding: 2px 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    position: relative;
}

.session-tasks li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 4px;
    color: var(--accent-aqua);
}

.retro-footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: var(--space-lg);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
}

@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .retro-metrics {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
    .writing-entry {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
    }
    .writing-type {
        display: none;
    }
}
</style>